column1: #Text=Concerning your punishment , you 've had a number of disagreements over the years with Senate leader David Long .
#Text=Does Senate leader David Long serve the Republicans in the state senate or do they serve him ?
#Text=: Yeah , that is a great question .
#Text=He and I every couple of years will have an issue .
#Text=The legislative process is not one where conflict can be avoided .
#Text=When you are in the arena , you are going to have issues , and I have enjoyed serving with Senator Long .
#Text=But ultimately we the people elect elected officials to serve in the legislative branch of government .
